nodes.text: Liquor was a strong alcoholic beverage, classified among the alcoholic beverages known as spirits. It was produced through processes of distillation (for example from fruit) and was often produced in a distillery factory. Liquor was quite expensive, and classified as a luxury good. Some people kept their bottles of liquor in a special liquor cabinet. The planet Seikosha was a major exporter of this beverage. Some types of liquor could be mixed with caf.
There were several types and brands of liquor, including spiced liquor, Idlewil liquor, lum, cognac, juri juice brandy, tihaar, namana liquor, tuber liquor, pulkay, whiskey and Twi'lek liquor.
